name: [0] // THE KEYS //
description: I have been collecting on HEN since the near beginnings of the platform and have connected with hundreds of artists and fellow collectors. HEN has changed my life and inspired me for the better. So how do I put a price on something I have invested so much time, effort, and passion into?  I don't know what the right answer is, but I do know if someone does buy this, it will allow me to quit my current job and use my engineering background to focus on contributing to this space for the better.
